WEBVTT

00:14.960 --> 00:15.560
Master.

00:16.600 --> 00:19.160
There's some progress on another matter.

00:20.600 --> 00:21.920
If the Marquis of Wu'an

00:22.440 --> 00:23.510
truly is alive,

00:24.070 --> 00:25.070
what should we do?

00:31.760 --> 00:34.320
That will be a blessing for Great Yin.

00:37.470 --> 00:39.670
There are palace intrigues up ahead

00:40.240 --> 00:43.280
and Prince Changxin's rebellion
looming behind.

00:43.840 --> 00:48.030
The Marquis of Wu'an
is a pillar of stability.

02:18.440 --> 02:23.610
[Pursuit of Jade]

02:23.690 --> 02:26.220
[Episode 10]

03:03.520 --> 03:04.280
Father,

03:04.590 --> 03:05.430
Mother.

03:10.310 --> 03:11.080
Don't cry.

03:16.200 --> 03:19.000
Master, who is buried
behind this nameless stele?

03:24.800 --> 03:26.480
Today is Father's birthday.

03:27.780 --> 03:29.110
Let's be happy.

03:29.840 --> 03:31.870
That way,
Father and Mother can be at peace

03:31.870 --> 03:33.270
watching us from heaven.

03:44.520 --> 03:47.240
Fan Erniu. Meng Lihua.

03:49.560 --> 03:50.360
Fan...

03:51.840 --> 03:54.300
Could they have been
using another surname?

03:55.750 --> 03:58.800
The current situation is complicated.

03:59.590 --> 04:02.190
So much helplessness lies beneath.

04:02.800 --> 04:04.400
When the time is right,

04:04.590 --> 04:06.750
I will tell you everything.

04:10.590 --> 04:11.870
It's been 16 years.

04:12.480 --> 04:16.649
It's time for the truth to come to light.

04:17.570 --> 04:19.790
Zheng, burn the paper money.

04:25.440 --> 04:27.400
There's still some paper money at home.

04:27.400 --> 04:30.060
When we get back,
burn some for your parents too.

04:33.659 --> 04:35.320
Does burning these things...

04:35.930 --> 04:37.070
really work?

04:40.980 --> 04:41.830
Of course.

04:43.750 --> 04:46.080
People burn paper money during festivals

04:46.880 --> 04:48.810
to tell their deceased loved ones

04:52.300 --> 04:53.900
that we still remember them.

04:54.600 --> 04:55.270
Wenkan,

04:55.780 --> 04:57.570
promise me one thing.

04:58.240 --> 05:01.180
If one day I'm gone,

05:01.390 --> 05:03.480
you must take good care of

05:03.480 --> 05:04.940
the two Fan sisters for me.

05:05.070 --> 05:07.450
Never let them get involved.

05:07.470 --> 05:09.300
Master, you are in such good health.

05:09.300 --> 05:10.430
Why say such things?

05:12.950 --> 05:14.270
That day will come.

05:15.310 --> 05:16.000
Promise me.

05:20.050 --> 05:21.010
I promise you.

05:26.850 --> 05:28.060
Don't burn so much.

05:41.680 --> 05:42.340
Don't move.

05:43.630 --> 05:45.830
♪ The scenery is as clear as me ♪

05:46.900 --> 05:48.100
♪ With very pale colors ♪

05:48.900 --> 05:51.860
♪ Just like the outline in the mirror ♪

05:52.320 --> 05:54.810
♪ I think that's me, being naive ♪

05:55.560 --> 05:56.890
♪ Unlocking my heart ♪

05:57.720 --> 06:01.880
♪ I hid you in my soul ♪

06:01.080 --> 06:04.630
You two look just like Father and Mother.

06:10.720 --> 06:11.810
Thanks.

06:13.520 --> 06:14.450
You're welcome.

06:24.870 --> 06:25.870
Come, Changning.

06:42.360 --> 06:44.020
What's wrong with your wrist?

06:44.110 --> 06:47.510
The ox cart tipped over
when I was collecting pigs yesterday.

06:47.630 --> 06:49.230
I used my hand to break the fall

06:49.230 --> 06:50.120
and sprained it.

06:50.120 --> 06:52.230
Changyu's wrist hurts often.

06:52.260 --> 06:54.310
Butchering pigs is tiring work.

06:59.190 --> 07:01.890
Constant strain on the wrist
over the years can lead to tendon pain.

07:01.890 --> 07:03.750
Luckily the bone isn't affected.

07:04.960 --> 07:07.570
But you need to be careful from now on.

07:11.220 --> 07:12.360
On the way back later,

07:12.360 --> 07:14.840
I'll get off at the grocery store
to buy something.

07:14.840 --> 07:16.330
You don't have money, right? Here.

07:16.330 --> 07:17.460
No need. I have some.

07:18.270 --> 07:19.670
How would you have money?

07:22.180 --> 07:23.380
Get in the cart first.

07:27.020 --> 07:29.160
Then you two go home first
after I'm done shopping.

07:29.160 --> 07:31.490
I'll go buy you some tangerine peel candy.

07:31.490 --> 07:32.040
Okay.

07:33.010 --> 07:34.500
Changyu is the best.

07:45.630 --> 07:46.159
You...

07:47.150 --> 07:48.600
People keep dying

07:48.600 --> 07:50.120
in Xigu Lane.

07:50.120 --> 07:51.270
Maybe we've provoked

07:51.270 --> 07:52.159
some kind of spirit.

07:52.159 --> 07:53.190
It's bad luck.

07:53.190 --> 07:53.870
Exactly.

07:53.870 --> 07:56.430
It seems this rice water isn't enough.

07:57.040 --> 07:57.750
In a moment,

07:57.750 --> 07:59.810
I need to find some dry mugwort leaves

08:00.750 --> 08:02.870
and hang them on this door.

08:03.070 --> 08:04.160
Exactly.

08:07.730 --> 08:09.530
Look at that jinx.

08:09.660 --> 08:10.600
Exactly.

08:10.600 --> 08:12.330
She was actually staring at us.

08:15.680 --> 08:16.630
You're back?

08:20.920 --> 08:21.920
What's wrong?

08:23.660 --> 08:24.950
You look listless.

08:27.270 --> 08:28.430
Why are you all wet?

08:29.270 --> 08:31.730
The snow was deep.
It must have been the snow.

08:37.000 --> 08:37.720
Wait.

08:43.510 --> 08:44.510
Was someone bullying you

08:44.510 --> 08:46.310
and saying bad things about you?

08:46.350 --> 08:48.300
Who dares to do that?

08:48.750 --> 08:50.210
I'd knock their teeth out.

08:51.030 --> 08:52.760
I'm going to change my clothes.

08:56.630 --> 08:59.880
[Xigu Lane]

09:04.120 --> 09:04.960
Fan Changyu!

09:05.550 --> 09:06.440
Fan Changyu!

09:06.750 --> 09:08.390
Come out here! Fan Changyu!

09:09.510 --> 09:10.960
Fan Changyu! You...

09:12.840 --> 09:13.570
Fan Changyu,

09:14.000 --> 09:15.290
your sister pushed our Hutou

09:15.290 --> 09:17.050
down the stairs at noon.

09:17.360 --> 09:18.080
Look.

09:18.600 --> 09:20.390
He lost two front teeth.

09:20.390 --> 09:22.000
Tell me,
what are you going to do about it?

09:22.000 --> 09:23.730
My sister has always been weak.

09:23.850 --> 09:26.380
Your grandson is years older than her.

09:27.270 --> 09:29.070
How could she possibly push him?

09:29.150 --> 09:29.550
Well...

09:29.550 --> 09:31.200
Granny Kang, let's talk this over calmly.

09:31.200 --> 09:33.860
You're making a scene
in front of the neighbors.

09:34.600 --> 09:36.200
The Fan family bullied my grandson.

09:36.200 --> 09:38.510
Why should I be afraid of
being laughed at?

09:38.510 --> 09:39.390
Isn't it normal for kids to have

09:39.390 --> 09:41.320
a few bumps and scrapes
when they're playing around?

09:41.320 --> 09:42.460
-Stop shouting.
-Whether you have the right

09:42.460 --> 09:44.120
to demand justice here or not,

09:44.270 --> 09:46.200
we need to ask Fan Changning first.

09:47.150 --> 09:48.870
Changning, come out.

09:53.120 --> 09:54.250
Come out. It's okay.

09:55.320 --> 09:56.670
Changning, come here.

09:58.150 --> 09:58.720
Come.

10:00.270 --> 10:02.030
Changyu wants to ask you something.

10:02.030 --> 10:02.750
Come here.

10:04.600 --> 10:05.320
Come.

10:06.240 --> 10:07.080
Let me ask you.

10:08.390 --> 10:09.450
Did you push Hutou?

10:12.600 --> 10:13.480
Look at that.

10:13.480 --> 10:15.360
Such a little child
already knows how to lie.

10:15.360 --> 10:16.480
She nodded just now,

10:16.480 --> 10:18.210
and now she's shaking her head.

10:19.000 --> 10:20.730
Fan Changning, I'm asking you.

10:20.750 --> 10:21.840
Don't lie.

10:21.840 --> 10:22.910
Lying will make your mouth rot.

10:22.910 --> 10:23.240
You know that?

10:23.240 --> 10:23.870
Get away!

10:27.750 --> 10:29.750
How dare you push me!

10:30.320 --> 10:32.480
Is there no justice left?

10:32.870 --> 10:35.600
The Fan family is so arrogant!

10:37.080 --> 10:39.200
They made my grandson like this,

10:39.200 --> 10:41.750
and... and she's acting
as if she's completely in the right!

10:41.750 --> 10:42.550
Stop shouting!

10:42.550 --> 10:43.240
Alright.

10:43.840 --> 10:44.870
See if I will shove your head

10:44.870 --> 10:46.130
into the swill bucket!

10:46.750 --> 10:47.960
I held back earlier

10:48.960 --> 10:50.030
because I didn't know

10:50.030 --> 10:51.490
who my family had offended

10:51.550 --> 10:53.240
to bring trouble to Xigu Lane.

10:53.550 --> 10:55.610
I feel guilty towards the neighbors,

10:55.720 --> 10:57.180
but I haven't wronged you.

10:57.840 --> 11:00.560
People keep dying in your family
these days.

11:00.790 --> 11:03.670
Everyone in the lane knows
that you jinxed them!

11:03.670 --> 11:06.120
You and Mrs. Song
gossip about me every day.

11:06.600 --> 11:08.000
Do you think I don't know?

11:09.030 --> 11:09.550
Fine.

11:13.750 --> 11:15.400
I'll grant your wish today.

11:17.030 --> 11:18.090
What are you doing?

11:19.240 --> 11:21.090
The neighbors are watching.

11:21.200 --> 11:22.960
Do you dare commit violence here?

11:22.960 --> 11:25.510
You've already ruined my reputation.

11:26.340 --> 11:27.630
You don't think I still care

11:27.630 --> 11:28.960
what they think, do you?

11:30.870 --> 11:32.600
If I really do something to you,

11:33.620 --> 11:35.280
do you think they'll help you?

11:43.030 --> 11:43.690
Changning.

11:45.960 --> 11:48.320
When I asked if you pushed Hutou just now,

11:49.120 --> 11:51.650
why did you nod first
and then shake your head?

11:53.840 --> 11:55.600
I did push him.

11:55.870 --> 11:58.120
But he was too fat.

11:58.440 --> 12:00.240
I couldn't move him.

12:00.870 --> 12:02.440
He chased me,

12:02.440 --> 12:05.250
fell down the stairs himself,

12:05.630 --> 12:07.820
and broke his front teeth.

12:07.850 --> 12:09.120
Hutou said you pushed him!

12:09.120 --> 12:09.870
Shut up!

12:09.870 --> 12:12.430
I knew Hutou fell on his own.

12:14.670 --> 12:15.840
Why did you push him?

12:17.320 --> 12:19.150
He pulled my hair,

12:19.860 --> 12:21.990
snatched my candy,

12:22.590 --> 12:25.230
threw rice water on me,

12:25.350 --> 12:28.380
and called me a jinx's sister,

12:29.240 --> 12:32.370
saying I needed a splash of water
to get rid of my bad luck.

12:36.080 --> 12:38.780
You filthy old hag who deserves
to be buried with no coffin!

12:38.780 --> 12:40.240
Not only do you have a wicked tongue,

12:40.240 --> 12:42.100
you don't even do good deeds
for your grandson.

12:42.100 --> 12:43.750
Aren't you afraid the King of Hell

12:43.750 --> 12:44.940
will rip your tongue out after you die?

12:44.940 --> 12:46.550
How am I wicked?

12:46.730 --> 12:48.520
Did I kill her parents?

12:48.780 --> 12:51.800
Did I kill all those people
who died in her family?

12:53.240 --> 12:55.200
Everyone in Lin'an knows

12:55.240 --> 12:57.020
she's a jinx!

12:57.480 --> 12:59.150
Only you and your husband,

12:59.150 --> 13:00.790
who have no one to bury you when you die,

13:00.790 --> 13:02.980
took in this whole cursed family.

13:03.080 --> 13:04.320
Maybe one day,

13:04.320 --> 13:06.250
she'll bring you to your death too.

13:08.480 --> 13:09.670
If you ask me,

13:09.670 --> 13:10.840
the Fan family

13:10.840 --> 13:12.910
should've gotten out
of Xigu Lane long ago.

13:12.910 --> 13:15.510
Who knows when their enemies
will come looking for them.

13:15.510 --> 13:18.200
-Why are you so mean?
-If I'm going to jinx anyone to death,

13:18.200 --> 13:20.200
you'll be the first one, you old hag.

13:20.840 --> 13:22.670
Why should I leave Xigu Lane?

13:23.440 --> 13:25.550
If you're so scared, you leave.

13:26.720 --> 13:27.380
And listen—

13:30.720 --> 13:31.670
if you ever

13:32.180 --> 13:34.820
lay a finger on Fan Changning again,

13:34.840 --> 13:37.040
whichever hand you use, I'll cut it off.

13:38.120 --> 13:39.950
You think I'm scared of you?

13:41.080 --> 13:42.360
Don't try to scare me.

13:43.490 --> 13:44.540
Scare you?

13:47.240 --> 13:50.100
I can chop a pig's trotter
clean off with one stroke.

13:50.840 --> 13:52.570
Your hand would be even easier.

13:53.270 --> 13:54.240
Left or right?

13:54.510 --> 13:56.110
Which one do you want to keep?

13:56.120 --> 13:57.720
-How about neither?
-Don't!

13:58.600 --> 13:59.320
Hutou!

14:00.720 --> 14:01.240
Hu...

14:02.360 --> 14:02.960
Grandma!

14:03.320 --> 14:04.390
Karma!

14:05.200 --> 14:06.470
This is instant karma!

14:06.630 --> 14:08.080
You saw that, right?

14:08.080 --> 14:09.550
Changyu and I didn't touch this old woman.

14:09.550 --> 14:11.080
She fell on her own.

14:11.820 --> 14:15.380
It was her! She kicked me!

14:17.030 --> 14:17.770
Granny Kang,

14:17.800 --> 14:19.520
we were all watching.

14:19.630 --> 14:20.860
You fell on your own.

14:20.880 --> 14:22.840
You must have been too vicious
with your words,

14:22.840 --> 14:24.200
so heaven punished you.

14:24.790 --> 14:25.510
Exactly.

14:26.080 --> 14:28.810
It was this jinx! She jinxed me!

14:28.840 --> 14:31.150
Get lost! Or I'll jinx you to death!

14:31.190 --> 14:32.110
Granny Kang,

14:32.110 --> 14:33.030
be careful.

14:33.030 --> 14:34.720
Or you may knock your teeth out.

14:34.720 --> 14:36.880
Don't blame Changyu for that too.

14:42.360 --> 14:43.030
Changning.

14:44.550 --> 14:46.970
in the future,
if anyone bullies you outside,

14:46.970 --> 14:48.700
come back and tell me, alright?

15:18.440 --> 15:19.660
How about you...

15:20.150 --> 15:21.550
not wait for the New Year?

15:22.400 --> 15:23.620
Just go now.

15:26.850 --> 15:29.050
Just because of a few words from others,

15:29.870 --> 15:31.270
you want to chase me away?

15:34.000 --> 15:35.280
My family's troubles

15:36.080 --> 15:38.220
have already dragged you in twice.

15:40.910 --> 15:42.840
You don't owe me anything anymore.

15:43.790 --> 15:46.240
If you cut ties with us sooner,

15:47.510 --> 15:48.600
you'll be safer.

15:56.840 --> 15:58.640
You believe that woman's words?

16:03.870 --> 16:04.510
No.

16:07.440 --> 16:08.770
I don't believe in fate,

16:09.750 --> 16:11.820
nor in that nonsense
about being a cursed star

16:11.820 --> 16:13.390
who brings misfortune.

16:14.270 --> 16:15.750
I just think that those people

16:15.750 --> 16:17.410
won't let my family go easily,

16:19.960 --> 16:22.090
so I don't want to drag you down with us.

16:22.400 --> 16:24.130
If you think you can push me away

16:25.120 --> 16:26.980
just because it's for my own good,

16:28.510 --> 16:30.040
then what about Changning?

16:30.770 --> 16:32.830
Are you going to cut ties with her too?

16:35.610 --> 16:36.260
I can't.

16:37.270 --> 16:38.240
She's too young.

16:39.100 --> 16:40.500
I have to keep her with me.

16:44.670 --> 16:45.480
So,

16:46.270 --> 16:48.470
you're only driving me away, is that it?

16:55.750 --> 16:58.410
You're not the type
to take an insult lying down.

16:59.080 --> 17:00.670
If someone splashes water on you,

17:00.670 --> 17:03.200
just teach them a lesson
right then and there.

17:06.160 --> 17:08.560
There's a saying
I once heard from Mr. Wang:

17:08.890 --> 17:10.950
"The law does not punish the masses."

17:11.720 --> 17:14.720
It means that if a large group of people
breaks the law,

17:15.099 --> 17:17.760
the authorities
usually won't punish them all.

17:18.349 --> 17:20.440
Now the whole town is gossiping about me

17:20.440 --> 17:21.740
behind my back.

17:22.400 --> 17:24.200
I might be able to deal with one of them,

17:24.200 --> 17:25.730
but can I deal with them all?

17:28.369 --> 17:30.100
[Young Xie Zheng]

17:34.720 --> 17:39.050
[Young Wei Xuan]

17:41.240 --> 17:42.990
Then have you ever heard of the saying

17:42.990 --> 17:44.650
"make an example of someone"?

17:45.070 --> 17:46.270
Human nature is evil.

17:46.640 --> 17:48.440
If you're weak and easy to bully,

17:48.630 --> 17:50.090
no matter how kind you are,

17:50.730 --> 17:52.170
no one will help you.

17:54.080 --> 17:55.840
But if you rise to power,

17:56.830 --> 17:58.680
even if you've done terrible things,

17:58.680 --> 18:01.010
plenty of people will rush to flatter you.

18:03.350 --> 18:06.340
Superstitions
are just meant to confuse people.

18:08.410 --> 18:10.870
Like the candy
that hit Granny Kang just now—

18:11.620 --> 18:12.640
in her eyes,

18:13.840 --> 18:15.770
it was just a ghost playing tricks.

18:17.620 --> 18:19.320
You can say these things to me,

18:20.350 --> 18:21.680
but if you start distancing yourself

18:21.680 --> 18:23.940
from Mr. Zhao and Mrs. Zhao because of it,

18:24.550 --> 18:26.010
they will be heartbroken.

18:31.390 --> 18:32.990
Then take what I said earlier

18:33.350 --> 18:34.750
as a moment of impulse.

18:36.160 --> 18:37.240
Please stay.

18:39.350 --> 18:40.750
So it's up to you

18:41.400 --> 18:43.000
whether I leave or stay, huh?

18:43.710 --> 18:44.970
You've got some nerve.

18:47.880 --> 18:49.400
Don't be mad.

18:50.070 --> 18:52.530
The candy I bought you
wasn't meant for that.

18:53.030 --> 18:55.200
You should have gone and found
some pebbles.

18:55.200 --> 18:56.640
Candy is expensive.

18:55.450 --> 18:57.650
♪ The scenery is as clear as me ♪

18:57.000 --> 18:58.060
It was not worth it.

18:58.720 --> 18:59.920
♪ With very pale colors ♪

19:00.720 --> 19:03.680
♪ Just like the outline in the mirror ♪

19:04.140 --> 19:06.630
♪ I think that's me, being naive ♪

19:07.380 --> 19:08.860
♪ Unlocking my heart ♪

19:07.920 --> 19:09.540
I never had the chance to ask before.

19:09.540 --> 19:13.700
♪ I hid you in my soul ♪

19:10.720 --> 19:13.650
Why did you become an armed escort
and risk your life?

19:15.560 --> 19:16.560
Because...

19:17.150 --> 19:19.620
♪ The moon is as quiet as me ♪

19:17.460 --> 19:19.320
there are things I simply must do.

19:20.240 --> 19:21.270
Just like how

19:20.420 --> 19:22.030
♪ The light shines ♪

19:21.290 --> 19:23.590
you want to keep running
your father's butcher shop.

19:22.720 --> 19:25.460
♪ It illuminates
the turbulence in my heart ♪

19:25.200 --> 19:26.070
My father

19:25.910 --> 19:28.520
♪ It seems to be the fire of love ♪

19:27.540 --> 19:29.140
also had unfinished business.

19:29.140 --> 19:30.880
♪ Just a few sparks ♪

19:30.640 --> 19:32.070
I want to finish it for him.

19:31.330 --> 19:36.210
♪ Let me hide in your heart ♪

19:35.960 --> 19:37.960
So your family ran an escort agency?

19:38.680 --> 19:40.400
And you were the Young Master?

19:38.740 --> 19:39.810
♪ I pray that our love ♪

19:39.840 --> 19:42.530
♪ Will never end ♪

19:41.640 --> 19:43.960
Rebuilding an escort agency
costs a lot of money.

19:43.200 --> 19:44.080
♪ It's worth my foolishly waiting ♪

19:44.100 --> 19:46.480
♪ For a lifetime ♪

19:44.920 --> 19:46.550
When I have some money to spare,

19:46.550 --> 19:47.980
I can help you out.

19:47.110 --> 19:51.150
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

19:48.400 --> 19:49.350
No need.

19:50.200 --> 19:51.510
I haven't repaid you

19:51.510 --> 19:52.680
for saving my life yet.

19:51.670 --> 19:55.170
♪ So what if we encounter difficulties? ♪

19:54.200 --> 19:56.050
That's a completely different matter.

19:56.050 --> 19:56.980
♪ I pray that our love
will not be like sand ♪

19:56.510 --> 19:58.300
When you agreed to marry into my family,

19:57.000 --> 19:59.510
♪ Slipping into the sea ♪

19:58.830 --> 20:00.200
we were already even.

20:00.790 --> 20:01.730
♪ I'd rather use this life ♪

20:01.750 --> 20:04.100
♪ To guard our love forever ♪

20:01.920 --> 20:03.380
You want to be even with me?

20:04.900 --> 20:08.790
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

20:07.100 --> 20:08.590
That's not what I meant.

20:09.270 --> 20:17.460
♪ Why do we need
to seek cause and effect ♪

20:20.270 --> 20:21.960
We've known each other for so long,

20:21.960 --> 20:24.420
yet I still don't know
when your birthday is.

20:25.160 --> 20:26.880
My birthday is easy to remember.

20:26.880 --> 20:28.400
It's 2 days after the Lantern Festival.

20:28.400 --> 20:30.110
The holiday spirit is still strong then.

20:30.110 --> 20:31.110
It's very lively.

20:31.960 --> 20:32.890
What do you want?

20:35.920 --> 20:38.920
I want my family all together,

20:38.920 --> 20:39.830
safe and sound.

20:40.720 --> 20:41.680
And if in the spring,

20:41.680 --> 20:45.340
I could keep another litter of piglets,
that would be even better.

20:52.200 --> 20:56.260
[Capital]

20:55.330 --> 20:57.940
Your Majesty, I have a proposal.

20:58.480 --> 21:00.110
Grand Tutor, please go ahead.

21:00.110 --> 21:00.920
Your Majesty,

21:01.270 --> 21:03.350
the weather has been erratic this year.

21:03.350 --> 21:05.880
The land is barren,
and the crops have failed.

21:06.270 --> 21:08.070
In this year of disaster,

21:08.510 --> 21:11.080
if we still transport grain
to the front line,

21:11.350 --> 21:13.270
I fear it will cause a refugee crisis

21:13.270 --> 21:15.400
and shake the foundation of the state.

21:16.200 --> 21:18.590
Your Majesty, I implore you

21:18.790 --> 21:21.400
to revoke the restoration order
for the front line.

21:21.400 --> 21:23.910
I humbly ask for Your Majesty's judgment.

21:24.400 --> 21:27.620
The situation on the front line
changes rapidly.

21:28.000 --> 21:31.110
Even the Marquis of Wu'an
has fallen in battle.

21:32.150 --> 21:35.680
Provisions before a great battle
are of the utmost importance.

21:36.070 --> 21:37.960
How can we easily revoke the order?

21:37.960 --> 21:39.830
After years of war,

21:39.830 --> 21:42.790
the treasury is now empty
and cannot bear the burden.

21:43.750 --> 21:46.350
If the treasury is empty,
levy grain locally

21:46.350 --> 21:48.070
to solve the urgent need.

21:48.350 --> 21:50.300
After we pacify Chongzhou,

21:50.440 --> 21:52.960
we can return it to the people.

21:53.260 --> 21:55.920
It is deep winter now,
and the end of the year is approaching.

21:55.920 --> 21:58.690
The people's surplus grain is not enough
to fill their own stomachs.

21:58.690 --> 22:00.160
Levying grain locally?

22:00.480 --> 22:01.610
Prime Minister Wei,

22:01.920 --> 22:03.560
are you not worried

22:04.030 --> 22:06.090
that it will incite a civil uprising?

22:06.350 --> 22:08.440
The front line is engulfed
in flames of war,

22:08.440 --> 22:10.680
and our soldiers
are fighting bloody battles.

22:10.680 --> 22:12.940
Provisions are the lifeline of the army.

22:13.000 --> 22:14.860
How can they go a day without them?

22:15.240 --> 22:18.960
If the enemy takes this chance
to march south and breach our cities,

22:18.960 --> 22:22.670
I fear it will bring disaster
and ruin to our nation.

22:23.000 --> 22:23.960
Grand Tutor,

22:24.510 --> 22:28.510
do you dare to bear
such a heavy responsibility alone?

22:29.310 --> 22:31.000
Surely, Grand Tutor Li,

22:31.000 --> 22:33.350
you do not wish to repeat the tragedy
of 16 years ago,

22:33.350 --> 22:35.960
when provisions
failed to reach Jinzhou City,

22:35.960 --> 22:38.690
leading to its massacre?

22:51.210 --> 22:52.930
Prime Minister Wei is farsighted.

22:52.930 --> 22:55.700
He is truly the most loyal subject
of Great Yin.

22:55.770 --> 22:59.620
[Diligent and Virtuous]

22:56.110 --> 22:58.510
Prime Minister Wei is loyal and righteous.

22:59.680 --> 23:03.660
[Wei Residence]

23:14.420 --> 23:15.100
Uncle,

23:15.480 --> 23:17.500
when I grow up,
I want to be like my father,

23:17.500 --> 23:19.160
fighting on the battlefield.

23:33.350 --> 23:35.470
[Mrs. Wei]

23:34.960 --> 23:35.890
Prime Minister.

23:37.960 --> 23:38.640
Come in.

23:47.720 --> 23:50.320
Prime Minister,
please have some ginseng tea.

23:54.890 --> 23:56.420
Have Zheng's remains

23:56.590 --> 23:58.240
still not been found?

24:02.480 --> 24:05.450
This child is of the Wei family's
bloodline.

24:05.480 --> 24:09.850
And he was raised with such care by you.

24:10.240 --> 24:12.970
They say a maternal uncle
is like a second father.

24:13.030 --> 24:15.950
It's such a pity that he died like this.

24:16.400 --> 24:19.070
Please take care of yourself,
Prime Minister.

24:22.590 --> 24:24.680
-And Xuan...
-Please go back.

24:28.000 --> 24:29.720
I spoke out of turn.

24:30.550 --> 24:32.810
I beg your forgiveness, Prime Minister.

24:37.670 --> 24:39.070
I shall take my leave.

25:07.830 --> 25:08.680
Prime Minister,

25:08.680 --> 25:10.310
He Jingyuan, Governor of Jizhou,

25:10.310 --> 25:12.310
has sent a brocade box by fast horse.

25:13.450 --> 25:18.240
[To Prime Minister Wei of Great Yin]

25:22.270 --> 25:24.580
He has always been cautious.

25:27.240 --> 25:31.150
[To Wei Qilin]

25:28.270 --> 25:29.330
To General Suituo,

25:30.070 --> 25:31.480
Jinzhou is in critical danger.

25:31.480 --> 25:33.200
I must return to the capital
for an urgent matter.

25:33.200 --> 25:35.070
Therefore, I am sending
my household general, Wei Qilin,

25:35.070 --> 25:38.380
to request immediate reinforcements
with the Tiger Tally

25:38.590 --> 25:39.750
to resist Beijue together

25:39.750 --> 25:41.690
and save Crown Prince Chengde.

25:42.030 --> 25:43.750
General, Wei Yan.

25:44.270 --> 25:47.330
Eighth day of the fifth month,
the 26th year of Taikang.

25:53.480 --> 25:55.790
It seems He Jingyuan

25:55.790 --> 25:58.600
is using his own life as leverage

25:58.720 --> 26:02.680
to make me spare the two daughters
of that traitor.

26:03.200 --> 26:04.580
He Jingyuan is so bold.

26:04.960 --> 26:07.460
Prime Minister, you shouldn't have been
soft-hearted back then

26:07.460 --> 26:09.920
and stopped searching
for Wei Qilin's body.

26:12.510 --> 26:13.510
Zheng's

26:14.000 --> 26:16.730
sudden investigation
into the Jinzhou massacre

26:17.440 --> 26:20.270
must have been instigated
by someone with ulterior motives.

26:20.270 --> 26:21.480
Now,

26:21.550 --> 26:24.030
even He Jingyuan goes against my orders.

26:24.200 --> 26:25.260
Why don't you let me

26:25.400 --> 26:27.000
go and get rid of He Jingyuan?

26:29.750 --> 26:32.310
The battle in Chongzhou
is critical right now.

26:32.310 --> 26:35.160
If I lose a weapon like He Jingyuan,

26:35.260 --> 26:37.190
the Northwest will be in peril.

26:38.480 --> 26:39.000
I see.

26:39.160 --> 26:40.030
Forget it.

26:40.070 --> 26:41.680
They are just two girls.

26:42.060 --> 26:46.120
[To Wei Qilin]

26:42.680 --> 26:43.480
Let them live.

26:44.110 --> 26:46.440
How much trouble can they possibly cause?

27:05.960 --> 27:06.960
Lord Li?

27:09.170 --> 27:15.620
[Fill Your Belly]

27:09.440 --> 27:11.200
Your husband is not home today?

27:12.510 --> 27:13.840
He went out on business.

27:14.590 --> 27:16.720
Do you need him for something, My Lord?

27:17.000 --> 27:18.260
Just asking casually.

27:18.510 --> 27:19.160
By the way,

27:20.400 --> 27:21.750
regarding the case involving your family,

27:21.750 --> 27:23.480
I have figured out everything.

27:23.770 --> 27:24.770
Who did it?

27:25.510 --> 27:28.000
The Qingzhou Government Office
found that the attacks on your family

27:28.000 --> 27:31.440
stemmed from an escort mission
your father undertook years ago.

27:31.440 --> 27:32.720
Rumor has it that it involved
a treasure map

27:32.720 --> 27:35.000
left by
the previous dynasty's royal family.

27:35.000 --> 27:36.160
Over a decade ago,

27:36.400 --> 27:38.730
everyone in the escort agency was killed.

27:38.830 --> 27:40.590
Only your father survived.

27:41.240 --> 27:44.570
That was why he could settle down here
in Lin'an Town all these years.

27:44.570 --> 27:46.370
After the turmoil in Chongzhou,

27:46.590 --> 27:48.720
the treasure map was brought up again.

27:48.850 --> 27:51.750
The bandits from Qingfeng Stronghold
tracked down your father,

27:51.750 --> 27:54.480
which is why
they repeatedly attacked your home—

27:55.150 --> 27:57.790
to get that treasure map.

27:58.200 --> 27:59.520
Treasure map?

28:01.680 --> 28:03.880
I've never heard my parents mention it.

28:04.640 --> 28:05.160
Yes.

28:06.680 --> 28:08.880
So, rumors can be deadly.

28:11.920 --> 28:14.110
Why did Li Huaian make up such a lie

28:14.110 --> 28:15.370
just to close the case?

28:19.350 --> 28:20.240
My parents...

28:21.640 --> 28:23.590
died just because of a rumor?

28:26.880 --> 28:30.170
A few days ago,
the rebels in Chongzhou announced

28:30.670 --> 28:33.110
that they had already found
the treasure map.

28:33.110 --> 28:35.240
The Qingfeng Stronghold bandits
won't come to town anymore.

28:35.240 --> 28:36.440
You can rest assured.

28:38.930 --> 28:41.670
[Memorial Tablet of Meng Lihua]
[Memorial Tablet of Fan Erniu]

28:43.480 --> 28:45.810
If there's a chance to catch those bandits

28:46.830 --> 28:48.630
and let my parents rest in peace,

28:48.670 --> 28:50.270
I am at your command, My Lord.

28:54.990 --> 29:02.420
[Fill Your Belly]

28:57.600 --> 28:58.650
This is the relief fund sent

28:58.650 --> 29:00.380
by Governor He of Jizhou, out of

29:00.590 --> 29:04.190
concern for the people.
He specially appointed me to deliver it.

29:08.640 --> 29:09.590
Is it all for me?

29:10.520 --> 29:13.000
For those who suffered at the hands
of the Qingfeng Stronghold bandits

29:13.000 --> 29:14.310
and lost family members,

29:14.310 --> 29:16.110
the government has issued
consolation money.

29:16.110 --> 29:17.570
It's not just your family.

29:18.030 --> 29:19.590
The standard is 10 taels per person.

29:19.590 --> 29:21.050
Here is 30 taels of silver.

29:21.720 --> 29:22.720
Please accept it.

29:31.200 --> 29:33.350
Dry weather!

29:34.000 --> 29:36.480
Beware of fire!

29:40.750 --> 29:41.830
It's flying over!

29:43.270 --> 29:44.420
Changyu,

29:44.510 --> 29:46.400
you talked in your sleep again last night.

29:46.400 --> 29:47.270
What did I say?

29:48.790 --> 29:52.510
You said you were afraid the spices
from out of town weren't authentic.

29:52.510 --> 29:53.590
You said,

29:53.590 --> 29:55.920
"Five spices aren't enough, we need six."

29:56.200 --> 29:58.940
Then you said that if Zheng left,

29:58.960 --> 30:02.600
you'd never find
such a handsome husband again.

30:07.240 --> 30:08.550
Keep your voice down.

30:11.270 --> 30:12.200
Changyu,

30:12.200 --> 30:14.130
we don't have to move anymore?

30:17.830 --> 30:20.880
But I already told the others
in the village

30:20.880 --> 30:22.010
that we were moving.

30:22.200 --> 30:24.400
It's so embarrassing not to move now.

30:25.310 --> 30:27.240
Can we move out for a little while,

30:27.240 --> 30:28.170
then move back?

30:28.200 --> 30:29.730
That would count as moving.

30:31.550 --> 30:33.030
Why are you so smart?

30:34.350 --> 30:35.200
How about this?

30:35.200 --> 30:36.240
Tell them

30:36.240 --> 30:37.640
we don't have to move anymore,

30:37.640 --> 30:39.060
and give them some candy.

30:39.240 --> 30:40.870
Then they won't laugh at you.

30:41.200 --> 30:42.070
Changyu,

30:42.070 --> 30:44.680
when will you go back to sleep with Zheng?

30:44.830 --> 30:46.690
You're squeezing into my small bed
every day.

30:46.690 --> 30:48.550
It's hard for me to even turn over.

30:49.070 --> 30:50.030
Mrs. Zhao says

30:50.030 --> 30:53.160
that a husband and wife
should sleep together for life.

30:54.830 --> 30:55.350
What?

30:55.640 --> 30:57.430
Are you sick of me already?

30:57.550 --> 30:58.340
I don't care.

30:58.480 --> 30:59.810
I want to sleep with you.

31:00.000 --> 31:01.420
For a lifetime!

31:02.510 --> 31:03.680
How dare you be sick of me!

31:03.680 --> 31:04.600
Take that!

31:04.880 --> 31:05.850
Are you still sick of me?

31:05.850 --> 31:07.440
-No!
-Are you?

31:07.870 --> 31:09.350
-No!
-Are you?

31:09.830 --> 31:10.960
You're not, are you?

31:11.110 --> 31:12.220
I yield.

31:13.270 --> 31:14.320
Beg for mercy, quickly!

31:14.320 --> 31:15.180
Changyu!

31:36.830 --> 31:37.830
All you do is eat.

31:38.720 --> 31:39.460
You're getting so fat.

31:39.460 --> 31:41.060
I wonder if you can still fly.

31:50.400 --> 31:50.960
Go now.

32:01.030 --> 32:04.050
[Xigu Lane]

32:04.070 --> 32:05.070
Let's go.

32:05.860 --> 32:06.600
Let's go!

32:18.750 --> 32:19.810
Morning, Mrs. Fan.

32:21.030 --> 32:21.960
Morning.

32:29.790 --> 32:31.070
Lord Li?

32:31.830 --> 32:33.560
Why are you at the Song's house?

32:34.520 --> 32:39.630
[Xigu Lane]

32:35.160 --> 32:37.640
I rented a vacant house from a broker.

32:37.640 --> 32:40.570
When I got here,
I realized it was opposite your home.

32:41.640 --> 32:43.240
So this family is named Song?

32:44.590 --> 32:46.320
Aren't you going back to Jizhou?

32:46.320 --> 32:47.480
I promised I would find

32:47.480 --> 32:49.140
the murderer of your parents.

32:49.160 --> 32:50.220
I must keep my word.

32:58.880 --> 32:59.830
Lord Li?

33:04.550 --> 33:06.310
To catch the murderer, Lord Li

33:06.330 --> 33:07.860
decided to stay for a while.

33:07.920 --> 33:09.920
And he even rented Song Yan's house.

33:10.270 --> 33:11.730
Isn't that a coincidence?

33:12.930 --> 33:14.460
What a coincidence indeed.

33:17.480 --> 33:18.810
I won't disturb you two.

33:31.960 --> 33:32.760
What's wrong?

33:32.830 --> 33:35.300
The falcon is gone.

33:38.590 --> 33:40.790
Maybe the lid
wasn't closed tightly last night.

33:40.790 --> 33:44.000
After its wings healed,
it flew away on its own.

33:44.510 --> 33:46.620
This falcon has parents of its own.

33:46.790 --> 33:48.740
It needs to go home to find them.

33:49.270 --> 33:50.030
Don't cry.

33:51.790 --> 33:53.260
There's nothing we can do.

33:53.440 --> 33:55.570
The falcon has a family too.

33:56.270 --> 33:57.720
Don't cry.

33:59.240 --> 34:00.480
It will fly back.

34:04.750 --> 34:07.960
Can you pinky-promise me for the falcon?

34:18.320 --> 34:20.449
You're going to leave sooner or later,

34:21.670 --> 34:22.360
aren't you?

34:24.360 --> 34:25.840
In my current situation,

34:26.630 --> 34:28.010
loving someone

34:28.710 --> 34:30.110
only puts them in danger.

34:35.440 --> 34:36.360
People

34:37.070 --> 34:39.850
are not deities
who cut off emotions and desires.

34:41.190 --> 34:42.360
It's hard to control

34:43.550 --> 34:44.630
your feelings.

34:51.280 --> 34:52.510
Don't coax her.

34:53.360 --> 34:55.090
Changning is just a bit lonely.

34:55.320 --> 34:57.440
I'll buy a cage of chicks in the spring.

34:57.440 --> 35:00.040
With new playmates,
she'll forget the falcon.

35:00.920 --> 35:01.920
In the spring,

35:01.920 --> 35:04.510
I'll buy you a big cage of chicks, okay?

35:04.760 --> 35:06.840
No. I want the falcon.

35:12.000 --> 35:12.590
You don't want that?

35:12.590 --> 35:13.800
I wasn't coaxing her.

35:14.920 --> 35:16.110
To fully tame a falcon,

35:16.110 --> 35:17.630
you have to let it fly first.

35:17.630 --> 35:18.830
Only one that returns

35:18.840 --> 35:20.360
is truly tamed.

35:23.150 --> 35:25.550
But there's no guarantee it
will come back.

35:33.980 --> 35:37.500
[Aspiring to the Clouds]

35:35.360 --> 35:37.420
So you're really not leaving Lin'an?

35:37.550 --> 35:38.760
I was so happy when I heard the news

35:38.760 --> 35:40.560
that I couldn't sleep all night.

35:40.590 --> 35:41.840
I'll show you something.

35:41.840 --> 35:43.360
I've been preparing it for a long time.

35:43.360 --> 35:45.070
-Come on.
-What is it?

35:47.920 --> 35:48.820
What are you doing?

35:48.820 --> 35:49.420
Look.

35:53.030 --> 35:54.860
The auspicious time has arrived!

35:54.860 --> 35:57.350
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

35:57.820 --> 35:59.410
[Braised Pork Belly] [Braised Pig's Ear]

35:59.450 --> 36:01.100
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

36:08.360 --> 36:09.660
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

36:14.150 --> 36:15.510
Bravo!

36:16.610 --> 36:19.670
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

36:27.110 --> 36:27.880
Pray to the God of Wealth,

36:27.880 --> 36:29.610
and may your business prosper!

36:42.190 --> 36:42.990
What's wrong?

36:44.280 --> 36:44.960
Nothing.

36:45.360 --> 36:46.760
Let's offer the incense.

36:48.740 --> 36:52.950
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

36:49.230 --> 36:51.960
Okay.

36:59.110 --> 37:00.320
What would you like to eat?

37:00.320 --> 37:01.920
Your meat smells delicious.

37:02.000 --> 37:03.480
I want a piece that's not too fatty.

37:03.480 --> 37:04.960
None of them is too fatty.
They're all good.

37:04.740 --> 37:06.630
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

37:05.320 --> 37:06.140
Pick a big one.

37:06.240 --> 37:06.920
Okay.

37:07.550 --> 37:08.750
I'll weigh it for you.

37:09.190 --> 37:10.030
Come back often.

37:10.030 --> 37:10.670
Okay.

37:11.190 --> 37:12.560
Changyu?

37:12.960 --> 37:14.100
It's me, it's me.

37:14.230 --> 37:16.650
Your shop has been closed for a while.

37:16.760 --> 37:18.960
We couldn't buy braised meat anywhere.

37:19.230 --> 37:22.090
Turns out you came to Yixiang Restaurant
to make it.

37:23.400 --> 37:24.190
Mrs. Fan

37:24.190 --> 37:26.320
is partnering with Yixiang Restaurant now.

37:26.320 --> 37:28.630
She'll sell exclusively here from now on.

37:28.630 --> 37:31.000
Ma'am, feel free
to come by anytime if you like it.

37:31.000 --> 37:33.430
Changyu's pork used to come

37:33.550 --> 37:35.110
with free offal.

37:35.400 --> 37:36.920
Then I won't be polite.

37:36.920 --> 37:37.940
Look at this.

37:38.030 --> 37:39.380
I... this...

37:39.410 --> 37:40.440
This time...

37:40.800 --> 37:41.880
Well, this time...

37:41.880 --> 37:43.510
Changyu's braised meat

37:43.510 --> 37:44.780
used to be home-style.

37:45.440 --> 37:47.510
Now that she's with Yixiang Restaurant,

37:47.510 --> 37:50.430
the ingredients and recipe are upgraded.

37:50.710 --> 37:52.100
Let alone offal,

37:52.280 --> 37:55.230
even the stock is pricier.

37:58.030 --> 37:59.030
Well,

37:59.280 --> 38:01.480
then how can we common folk afford that?

38:02.800 --> 38:03.760
Forget it.

38:03.880 --> 38:05.630
I'll look elsewhere.

38:05.630 --> 38:07.230
We are opening today,

38:07.230 --> 38:08.550
so we want to start on a lucky note.

38:08.550 --> 38:09.810
If you

38:10.070 --> 38:11.710
can bring us 5 customers in the future,

38:11.710 --> 38:13.570
you'll get a 20 percent discount.

38:13.590 --> 38:15.390
25 percent off for 10 customers.

38:15.550 --> 38:17.810
And 30 percent off for 20. How about that?

38:18.630 --> 38:19.230
Alright.

38:20.840 --> 38:22.110
Changyu,

38:22.110 --> 38:23.660
pick two good pieces of meat for me.

38:23.570 --> 38:25.780
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

38:23.710 --> 38:25.840
It's my husband's birthday today.

38:26.150 --> 38:26.760
Okay.

38:28.360 --> 38:30.760
I guarantee it'll be delicious
and generous.

38:30.760 --> 38:31.510
That piece.

38:40.630 --> 38:41.880
I didn't want to offer free offal before,

38:41.880 --> 38:44.030
and the customers
were unwilling to accept it.

38:44.030 --> 38:44.960
You just said a few words,

38:44.960 --> 38:46.630
and they rushed to give us money.

38:46.630 --> 38:49.360
Qianqian,
you're really amazing at doing business.

38:49.360 --> 38:50.930
Undercutting isn't business.

38:50.930 --> 38:53.460
Mutual benefit
is what business is all about.

38:59.590 --> 39:01.230
The great man is he who is in harmony,

39:01.230 --> 39:03.560
in his attributes, with heaven and earth;

39:03.760 --> 39:06.020
in his brightness, with the sun and moon;

39:06.030 --> 39:08.710
in his orderly procedure,
with the four seasons;

39:08.710 --> 39:09.770
and in his relation to
what is fortunate and what is calamitous,

39:09.770 --> 39:11.300
with the spiritual beings.

39:12.110 --> 39:13.230
He naturally—

39:33.150 --> 39:34.480
Your Lordship honors me
with your presence.

39:34.480 --> 39:35.800
My wait was not in vain.

39:38.110 --> 39:41.240
Tell me. What is your purpose
in coming to the Fan family?

39:44.030 --> 39:45.290
I came to the Fan family

39:45.710 --> 39:47.440
only to see you, Your Lordship.

39:51.400 --> 39:53.660
We have known each other since childhood

39:53.710 --> 39:56.310
and both learned martial arts
from General He.

39:57.920 --> 40:00.110
Since the conflict between the Li and Wei,

40:00.110 --> 40:01.960
we've been avoiding each other.

40:03.110 --> 40:03.960
It has been

40:04.480 --> 40:05.880
over a decade, hasn't it?

40:09.070 --> 40:10.710
I am curious now.

40:11.280 --> 40:12.280
Are you a Li

40:12.920 --> 40:13.960
or a Wei?

40:45.880 --> 40:47.100
I only serve Great Yin

40:48.030 --> 40:48.890
and the people.

40:51.230 --> 40:52.960
What about you, Your Lordship?

40:53.550 --> 40:54.950
Which side are you on now?

40:55.910 --> 40:56.920
Anyone can say

40:57.150 --> 40:58.070
pretty words.

41:02.150 --> 41:03.550
I have always

41:03.630 --> 41:04.760
only served myself.

41:06.880 --> 41:09.430
The conflict between Li and Wei
has become chaotic.

41:09.430 --> 41:12.550
And you intend to establish
your own faction in the future.

41:12.550 --> 41:15.670
Do you wish to make this chaos even worse?
